563
00:37:48,990 --> 00:37:53,720
Haiyao will have a great changeover with them.

564
00:37:53,720 --> 00:37:57,820
Once Haiyao makes a sensation with its new line of products,

565
00:37:57,820 --> 00:38:01,100
